{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 317045, "create_time": 1658995396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "先用干毛巾擦一下，用吹风的时候一手吹一手拨头发，可以把头发拿起落下，像理发店小哥吹的时候那样，可能会快点", "timestamp": 1658995396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 317046, "create_time": 1658995424, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "就是要吹很久，尤其有1000w限制", "timestamp": 1658995424}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 317069, "create_time": 1658996372, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "用毛巾擦，擦差不多就让他自然干", "timestamp": 1658996372}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 317096, "create_time": 1658997172, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "买一个干发帽，就直接tb搜干发帽，洗完头先把干发帽带一会儿，然后半干了再吹头发，吹的时候用手拨一拨，然后再晾一晾就好了", "timestamp": 1658997172}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 317121, "create_time": 1658998371, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "我也留过长发，从来不吹头发。", "timestamp": 1658998371}], "create_time": 1658994738, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658998371, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 5, "pid": 89863, "poll": null, "reply": 5, "text": "dz是个男孩子，最近几个月开始留长发\n现在发现一个很大的问题是\n洗完头后头发很难干\n用吹风机要吹好久\n以前从未留过头发所以很不适应\n所以。。求问女生们\n这是因为我吹头发的手法不对还是因为就是要吹好久啊QAQ\n有没有能让头发快点干的方法啊QAQ", "timestamp": 1658994738}}